Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:24.15,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,你嘟着嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:31.04,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,表情里看出了小九九
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:36.33,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,因为那份若即若离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:46.22,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,被你藏到了口袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:53.18,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,回忆是黑白照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:58.40,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,为它添上颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:06.95,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,再一次来到我的身边吧
